These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, filmmaking, baking, reading
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, thriller, spy, musical
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, sailing, climbing, snowboarding
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, bike, ship, tram
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the person who's sport is surfing##8
 2. the person driving the train is not to the left of the person driving the train##8
 3. the person driving the tram is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is surfing is not to the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##8
 5. the person driving the train is not to the right of the person driving the train##8
 6. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
 8. the person watching musical movies is between the person driving the bike and the person who's sport is sailing##2
 9. the person driving the tram is the person watching spy movies##1
10. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
11. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
12. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5
13. the person watching spy movies is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8
14. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person driving the ship##1
15. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not the person who's sport is sailing##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | fishing     | filmmaking   | reading | baking |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | musical   | comedy   | spy  |
| Sport         | sailing  | climbing  | snowboarding  | surfing |
| Transport     | train    | ship | bike     | tram    |

