.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, almond-milk, iced-tea, soy-milk
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, grapefruit, zucchini, papaya
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, classical, rock, dubstep
4 different pets are kept: fish, guinea-pig, goat, lizard
 1. the fan of rock is between the owner of the fish and the fan of classical##2
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##8
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person eating nectarine##3
 4. the person drinking coffee is not to the right of the owner of the lizard##8
 5. the owner of the fish is not to the left of the fan of classical##8
 6. the person eating papaya is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8
 7. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5
 8. the owner of the goat is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of reggae is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
10. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
11. the owner of the fish is not to the left of the fan of rock##8
12. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
13. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapefruit##5
14. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
15. the person drinking coffee is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
17. the person drinking coffee is not to the right of the fan of classical##8
18. the person eating grapefruit is not to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##8
19. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | coffee | iced-tea | soy-milk  | almond-milk  |
| Food          | papaya     | grapefruit | nectarine | zucchini  |
| Music-Genre   | classical    | rock  | dubstep | reggae |
| Pet           | goat | lizard | fish    | guinea-pig  |

