.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, singing, cooking, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, horror, comedy, crime
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, soul, classical, dubstep
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, weightlifting, cricket, parkour
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 2. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
 3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the left of the person watching crime movies##5
 4. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the right of the fan of r&b##5
 5. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the right of the person watching superhero movies##8
 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not to the left of the person watching comedy movies##8
 7. the fan of classical is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 9. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
10. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far right##1
11. the person watching superhero movies is not to the left of the fan of soul##8
12. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | collecting    | woodworking   | cooking | singing |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero     | comedy  | crime   | horror      |
| Music-Genre   | soul | r&b    | classical      | dubstep       |
| Sport         | cricket    | rowing | parkour   | weightlifting    |

