The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, photographer, project-manager, nurse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, water-polo, lacrosse, cricket
 1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the dressmaker##6
 2. the nurse is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
 3. the person eating cauliflower is the project-manager##1
 4. the person eating radish is between the dressmaker and the photographer##2
 5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
 6. the person who's sport is biathlon is not to the right of the person eating radish##8
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
 9. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the nurse##1
10. the photographer is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
11. the person who's sport is water-polo is not to the right of the person eating lettuce##8
12. the dressmaker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
13. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
14. the photographer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
15. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
