 4. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5
 5. the person driving the tram is the polish##1
 6. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the egyptian##8
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is not the british##6
 8. the security-guard is somewhere between the person driving the tram and the person drinking soy-milk##7
 9. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the right of the security-guard##5
10. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
11. the analyst is on the right of the mechanic##1
12. the security-guard is not the indian##6
13. the egyptian is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
14. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
15. the person driving the subway is not to the right of the security-guard##8

