.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate, 7up, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, rock, jazz, trance
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, baseball, rowing, basketball
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, van, airplane, jet-ski
 1. the person drinking 7up is the person who's sport is basketball##1
 2. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person driving the jet-ski##5
 4. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3
 6. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 8. the person driving the van is not to the right of the person who's sport is baseball##8
 9. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the right of the fan of rock##8
11. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person driving the jet-ski is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is baseball##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | juice   | soy-milk     | 7up    | hot-chocolate |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | trance      | jazz     | rock     |
| Sport         | handball | rowing  | basketball     | baseball  |
| Transport     | roller     | airplane | jet-ski | van     |

