.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade, 7up, mirinda
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, reading, hiking, board-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, funk, jazz, soul
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, thai, pakistani, indonesian
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the indonesian##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##8
 3. the person drinking mirinda is the fan of funk##1
 4. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 5. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the fan of soul##5
 6. the person who's hobby is hiking is not to the left of the fan of classical##8
 7. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 8. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
 9. the thai is not to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##8
10. the fan of jazz is not the japanese##6
11. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
12. the indonesian is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
13. the fan of soul is not to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##8
14. the japanese is on the right of the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | almond-milk      | mirinda  | 7up | lemonade        |
| Hobby         | board-games | reading   | sudoku   | hiking |
| Music-Genre   | soul    | funk   | jazz    | classical      |
| Nationality   | thai   | indonesian | pakistani   | japanese    |

