.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, water, tea, almond-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, entrepreneur, fisherman, scientist
4 different pets are kept: turtle, fish, rat, bird
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, bike, tram, train
 1. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 2. the owner of the bird is not to the right of the entrepreneur##8
 3. the owner of the turtle is the person drinking lemonade##1
 4. the person driving the tram is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 5. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
 6. the person driving the train is the person drinking water##1
 7. the scientist is not to the right of the person driving the train##8
 8. the fisherman is on the far right##1
 9. the entrepreneur is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
10. the person driving the motorbike is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the owner of the bird##5
12. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5
13. the person driving the tram is not to the left of the scientist##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1        |    2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | water          | lemonade | tea        | almond-milk    |
| Job         | scientist | manager   | entrepreneur | fisherman  |
| Pet         | rat           | turtle     | bird       | fish  |
| Transport   | train            | tram   | bike     | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, mirinda, soy-milk, milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, traveling, board-games, baking
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, journalist, mechanic, software-developer
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, train, car, trike
 1. the person who's hobby is board-games is not the person drinking soy-milk##6
 2. the bartender is not to the left of the person driving the trike##8
 3. the person who's hobby is baking is the person driving the train##1
 4. the bartender is not to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##8
 5. the journalist is somewhere to the right of the mechanic##5
 6. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 8. the person drinking tea is not to the left of the mechanic##8
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
10. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere between the person driving the trike and the software-developer##7
11. the person driving the car is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |      2       |       3       |    4    |
| Beverage    | soy-milk        | mirinda        | tea        | milk   |
| Hobby       | traveling      | woodworking      | baking | board-games |
| Job         | software-developer | mechanic | journalist     | bartender  |
| Transport   | car          | scooter      | train     | trike  |

