.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, skydiving, rock-climbing, puzzles
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, mechanic, dressmaker, photographer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, time-travel, sports, musical
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, blues, electronic, disco
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not to the left of the librarian##8
 2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 3. the fan of disco is somewhere to the right of the fan of electronic##5
 4. the photographer is the person watching musical movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the dressmaker##6
 6. the person watching action movies is not to the right of the fan of blues##8
 7. the person watching time-travel movies is not to the left of the dressmaker##8
 8. the dressmaker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
 9. the fan of electronic is in an even position##4
10. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
11. the person watching action movies is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the dressmaker and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
13. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | puzzles    | rock-climbing   | drawing   | skydiving |
| Job           | librarian | mechanic    | dressmaker | photographer    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports   | action | time-travel     | musical    |
| Music-Genre   | country   | electronic      | blues         | disco     |

 